Results.ReviewText: I've been drinking decaff coffee for a while, I like Nescafe Gold Blend decaff as it doesn't leave sludge at the bottom of the cup like some do also it has a fresh rounded flavour you would expect from a higher price coffee. I use it with soya as I'm dairy intolerant and it still keeps it's lovely flavour.
Results.Title: Nice flavour and reasonable price

Results.ReviewText:
Having tried numerous decaff coffees, I have concluded this is definitely the best.  It still has a very nice, rich, rounded, full flavour which is often missing in other decaffs.
In fact friends who normally drink regular coffee were unaware that this was the decaff version of their favourite coffee.
Results.Title: Best decaff

ClientResponses.Response: It's disappointing to hear you're not a fan of the changes we've made. Due to the addition of micro ground coffee during the recent change there may be a residue at the bottom of your cup now. Micro ground coffee is non-soluble coffee and gives you a similar experience to that of a barista made coffee! We've made a note of your comments & will be passing them to the rest of the team.

Results.ReviewText: It's hard to find a really tasty decaf coffee and the old Gold Blend was one product I really enjoyed.  However the new Gold Blend falls far short of my expectations.  It has very little taste and I don't like the residue it leaves in the bottom of my cup.  I will not be buying this product again.
Results.Title: Bring back the old Gold Blend

Results.ReviewText: This coffee is very reasonably priced but don't be put off by that.  It tastes lovely and smooth and has a full bodied taste than I have not found in other decaffs.  It is so good that my husband who is not usually a fan of decaffeinated coffee is drinking it too. Try it and see, you'll love it.
Results.Title: Beats the competition hands down

Results.ReviewText: With my girlfriend being pregnant, she had to cut out the caffeine but still wanted her regular coffees so we tried Nescafe Gold Blend Decaff and found it to be excellent. Great taste as you'd expect from Nescafe Gold Blend, a great cup but without the caffeine. So good that we both drank it.
Results.Title: all the taste, less the caff

Results.ReviewText: Have just bought this and I'm hooked already. The taste is so much more smooth than my normal brand. I made a cup for my neighbour and she has now bought a jar as she liked it so much. It is good value in comparison to my old brand. It is not at all bitter, just a perfect cup of coffee.
Results.Title: decaff delish!

Results.ReviewText: having been told by the doctor to cut down on my coffee intake,i thought id try the decaff version of the gold blend i usually drink to see if i could tell the difference and hand on heart i havent noticed any taste difference so im sold by the flavour so decaff is the future for me
Results.Title: gold blend decaff

Results.ReviewText: We love our coffee, but can only tolerate decaff.  I buy Nescaff decaff all the time, and enjoy it both at home and at work!  Everyone always says that decaf coffee doesn't have any flavour, but Nescafe Decaff is full of flavour, with a real nutty taste!  Thanks for a great drink!
Results.Title: Love Nescaff decaff!

ClientResponses.Response: Thanks for getting in touch & leaving your thoughts on the new recipe. It's sad to hear you're not a fan but we appreciate your feedback.

Results.ReviewText: Please bring back the old brand. We only drink black coffee and have used Gold Blend for many many years but not anymore. This new coffee is weak, has a bitter taste and there is no aroma. It is like a cheap brand of coffee and not up to the Nescafe standard.  Very disappointing.
Results.Title: Out with the NEW in with the OLD

Results.ReviewText: i love coffee, simple as that - only i drink too much of it and at night i lay awake for hours!  After trying this decaf, i can sleep like a baby! so not only is this wonderful decaf so very tasty, its also great for my mood, skin and well being! thankyou, thankyou, thankyou!!!
Results.Title: perfect decaf!

Results.ReviewText: I've recently been diagnosed with high potassium, so I had to stop drinking so much coffee. I love my coffee! Then I discovered Nescafe Gold Blend Decaf.  I tried several other brands but didn't like the taste. But Gold Blend Decaf is perfect. Great taste and low in potassium!
Results.Title: Delicious!

Results.ReviewText: We have been drinking this a few months now due to me being advised to drink only decaff coffee because of medication and suffering side effects of Insomnia.  I must admit both my Husband and I feel a lot better since changing to this coffee and would drink nothing else now.
Results.Title: Love it...

Results.ReviewText: This is a delicious 'decaff' coffee. It has none of the normal disadvantages - it tastes exactly the same as the 'proper' version, rich and rounded, but doesn't keep you awake, or affect sensitive folk like me. A wonderful choice if you suffer from problems sleeping.
Results.Title: Rich and Delicious

Results.ReviewText: I bought this as a replacement for my usual coffee that was out of stock, a very fortuitous event! This is smooth and full flavoured, I tend to drink my coffee on the weak side but this loses none of it's flavour by doing so - and makes it very good value for money.
Results.Title: Smooooooooth

Results.ReviewText: It took me a good while to find the perfect decaff coffee I first tasted Nescafe Gold Blend Decaff at a friends and since then I have not looked back. I love the smooth taste I can drink it black or with milk and best of all I have a good nights sleep no waking up!
Results.Title: The Best Decaff

Results.ReviewText: It smelt like a great coffee & tasted like a great coffee ... I ask for the name of the brand in order to buy it myself and then I get hit with " Its a Decaff " ..... Hmmmmm - I smell a rat ! No Way . Awesome coffee and Decaff  .... my prayers have been answered !
Results.Title: I smell a rat ......

Results.ReviewText: I bought this a while ago and after so many different coffees this has come out by far the best. I now carry a jar of this everywhere and take it all around my travels.. I even make my friends coffee and they say how nice the coffee is not realising it is de caff.
Results.Title: Excellent Service

ClientResponses.Response: Hi, we really value all our consumers feedback regarding the changes so thank you for getting in touch & letting us know your thoughts. We've added micro ground coffee to the recipe, to give it a more well rounded taste. This coffee is non-soluble and gives you a similar experience to that of a barista made coffee!

Results.ReviewText: I unwittingly bought a new jar without realising the recipe had changed,  just a new design for the jar I thought! It is TASTELESS and the residue at the bottom of the cup is HORRIBLE. Having to look for a new brand now, come on Nestlé,  bring back the original!
Results.Title: Tasteless

Results.ReviewText: I always prefer to drink decaff coffee and have tried all the major brands but honestly have to say that Nescafe Gold Decaff tops the lot! It has just the right amount of body and doesn't  artificial like many of the other decaff coffees around. Simply the best!
Results.Title: Simply the best!

Results.ReviewText: I have always bought equal amounts of Gold Blend and Gold Blend decaffeinated. Half caff became like hens' teeth, so I mix my own. I get all the lovely taste of Gold Blend without the caffeine hit that an avid coffee drinker perhaps wants to avoid over 24 hours.
Results.Title: Decaffeinated answer to my needs

Results.ReviewText: I love the strong taste of this coffee, it has a well rounded 'proper' coffee taste.  One rounded teaspoon per cup is enough for a great tasting coffee. Friends who I have given a cup of this to did not now it was decaff and were quite suprised how nice it was.
Results.Title: Gold Blend Decaff

Results.ReviewText: I always head for the decaff just because I like it better but the taste of this one was like coming home to my best friend, it was so welcoming. I couldn't wait to get home from work and taste my comforting beverage again and once more, it did not disappoint.
Results.Title: My real favourite decaff!

Results.ReviewText: Hi brought  Nescafe gold blend Decaff as have Barretts Disease, and must cut back on caffeine, have tried a few others and have found that Nescafe tastes really great and no caff for me means I can continue to have my coffee with out the worry, thanks Nescafe.
Results.Title: One of the best

Results.ReviewText:
Its so difficult to find a nice instant decaff coffee when you love coffee as much as I do. 
Unfortunately I cant drink caffeine anymore, so Ive been trying to find an instant decaff that lives up to my standards, the Gold Blend Decaff definitely does that.
Results.Title: The Decaff for coffee lovers

Results.ReviewText:
I've been trying a range of decaffeinated coffees lately and not really found one that i liked compared to the full caffeine varieties... until i tried this one.

Really liked the aroma, and the taste was just what i was looking for, a good strong flavour.
Results.Title: Very pleasantly surprised!

Results.ReviewText: I always buy the decaff version because i love waking up in the morning to enjoy a real cup of coffee for the rich taste and fragrant aroma, not only do i get a good nights sleep as it's decaff, i get to wake up the next morning and drink it all over again!
Results.Title: Great taste and aroma

ClientResponses.Response: Hi, thanks very much for letting us know your thoughts on the new recipe. We really appreciate your feedback! The residue you can see at the bottom of your cup is micro ground coffee that was added to NESCAFÉ Gold Blend during the recent change. This is non-soluble coffee and gives you a similar experience to that of a barista made coffee!

Results.ReviewText: What have you done to Nescafé Gold? It is bitter and leaves a residue in the bottom of the mug.  Why change something that was so good. I have found an alternative and will not be buying Nescafé Gold Blend again unless it reverts to the original recipe.
Results.Title: Never again!

Results.ReviewText: I tasted this for the first time at work about 6 weeks ago. I usually avoid coffee because I find it too strong and harsh, but I found Nescafe Gold Blend decaff to be smooth, and flavoursome with no harsh after effects. This is now my coffee of choice.
Results.Title: Great taste every time

Results.ReviewText: My husband loves coffee, but it does not like him, leaving him with a sickly feeling and dizziness-even  decaffs,  He tried Nescafe gold blend decaff and BINGO, great taste and the only one with no side effects, he sings it's praises to all and sundry.
Results.Title: The only one

Results.ReviewText: I couldn't get my normal brand and brought Nescafe Gold Decaff instead. I was so pleasantly surprised, I don't think I will be going back to my normal brand. It had the perfect flavour and made the best cup of evening coffee I have had in a long time.
Results.Title: Taste's awesome
